<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.7">
<l>parantiṭṭu niṉṟa paṭukaṭal taṉṉai</l>
<l>yirantiṭṭa kaimmē leṟitirai mōta</l>
<l>karantiṭṭu niṉṟa kaṭalaik kalaṅka</l>
<l>carantoṭṭa kaikaḷāl cappāṇi cārṅkaviṟ kaiyaṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the hands that discharged arrows to agitate the ocean,</l>
<l>that had remained hidden, so that the waves crashed,</l>
<l>striking the hands that beseeched the deep ocean</l>
<l>that remained spread out [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
<l>You with the hands [that bear] the śārṅga bow, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
